      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥna Tehwozis/ tahs\njaunas Seewas Tehws/ ustur-\nreja wiꞥnu/ ka tas trihs Deenas\npee wiꞥna palikke/ untee ehde un\ndsehre/ un palikke tur pahr Nakti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un zettortâ Deenâ steidsehs\ntee agri/ un zehlahs prohjam eet.\nTad jazzija tahs jaunas Seewas\nTehws us fawu Snohtu: Stip-\nrini tawn Sirdi ar weenu Mai-\nses Kummofju / un tad warrat\njuhs eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad apsehdehs tee/ un ehde\nabbi kohpâ un dsehre / un tahs\njannas Seewas Tehws jazzija\nus to Wihrs : Darri/ luhdsans/\ntik labbi/ un paleez zaur Nakti /\nun lai tawa Sirds eelihoimojahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas Wihrs zehlahs\nprohjam eet/ tad turreja to lohti\nwiꞥna Tehwozis/ ka tam bij at-\ngreestees/un tur pahrNakti palikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad nu wiꞥsch peektâ Dee-\nud agri steidsehs no-eet/ tad faz-\nzija tahs jaunas Seewas Tehws:\nStiprini jelle tawn Sirdi / un\ntee kawejahs kamehr ta Deena\nnolehze/ untee abbi ehde kohpâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tas Wihrs no-\neet/ wiꞥsch un wiꞥna leeka See-\nwa/ un wiꞥna Puifis. Bet\nwiꞥna Tehwozis/ tahs jaunas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tas Wihrs ne gri-\nbeja pahr Nakti palikt/ bet wiꞥ-\nzehlahs/ un nogahje / un nah-\nprett Jebus/ ta irr Jerusaleme\nun ar wiꞥnu tas pahris apkra-\ntu Ehsetu/ un wiꞥna leeke Se-\nwa ar wiꞥnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad nu tee pee Jebus bij-\ntad jaw bij uowakkarejees/ unt-\nPuifis jazzija us fawu Kungu\nDsenn luhdsans/ ka mehs fchi-\nnf Jebusitern Pilsfahta warra-\nmahjoht/ un eekch ta pahr Na-\nti palikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet wiꞥna Kungs jazz-\nja us wiꞥnu: Mehs ne gribba-\ngreestees us kahdu swechu Pil-\nshtu/kus ne irr no Israëta Beh-\nneem/ bet mehs gribbam pahrsta-\ngaht lihds Gibeju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad jazzija wiꞥsch us f-\nwu Puifi : Dsenn / ka mehs u-\nweenu no fchahm Weetahm na-\nkam/ un eekch Gibejas jeb Ra-\nmas pahr Nakti paleekain.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta gabje tee prohjam/ un-\nstaigaja/ un ta Saule nogah-\nteem/ itt klahtu pee Gibejas/ ka-\nBenjaminam peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Untee greesahs us turre-\nka tee nahktu/ un eekch Gibeja-\n"
    }
  ],
